  "title": "Facade Designer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job description:</strong></p><p>· Able to draw facade shop drawings and design sketches.</p><p>· Attend necessary design meetings to resolve design issues and present design proposal</p><p>· Coordinate with Client, Main Contractor, Architect and Consultants for design & technical concerns.</p><p>· Raise RFIs for any design / technical concerns / issues</p><p>· Provide technical advice to team</p><p>· Submit shop drawings and follow up the approval.</p><p>· Monitor the shop drawing and approval schedule.</p><p>· Monitor the design changes or additional scope of work.</p><p>· Support the project team for any site issues when necessary.</p><p>· Report to Design Manager</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><p>· Diploma/ Degree in architecture, design, engineering-related discipline</p><p>· Fresh graduate are welcome to apply</p><p>· Proficient in AutoCAD software and generally use Revit, Microsoft office / excel.</p><p>· Able to perform task under pressure and totally committed to follow through the tasks given within tight schedules</p><p></p>",
